GUIDELINES TO BE FOLLOWED WHILE CORRECTING THE FILES

Use the following notations in place of accented letters when a suitable keyboard is unavailable:

’

ā > a_

ã > a~

ā̃ > a_~

ē > e_

ẽ > e~

ē̃ > e_~

ī > i_

ĩ > i~

ī̃ > i_~

ō > o_

õ > o~

ō̃ > o_~

ū > u_

ũ > u~

ū̃ > u_~

ṅ > n0   (n zero)

ń > n/   (n slash)

ḍ > d#

ṛ > r#

ṭ > t#

ṇ > n#
